{"tid":1210201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 要善用人數優勢","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:04.000Z","uid":139484,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09adab2a711ba2bda293109172953b2e054fea56","tid":1210201,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"和理非非嘉年華 103萬人 政府完全唔care<br />\n今日包圍立法會 佔領夏𢡱道 雖然人數比狗壓倒性地多<br />\n不過只有少部分人敢衝 大部分人都係物資同撐場多<br />\n狗一放tear gas 敢衝嘅同唔敢衝嘅距離愈拉愈大<br />\n得返少部分人同狗硬碰<br />\n啲唔敢衝嘅人其實冇發揮到最大作用<br />\n<br />\n而且今日狗真係癡撚左線 再有同樣佔據陣地 同狗硬碰硬嘅活動 相信各位唔敢衝嘅戰友都可能會縮 會怕 唔適合打持久戰<br />\n<br />\n而要令香港人嘅人數優勢發揮功效，自然就係要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427ce3e42fbf7c6cc437f6ea118ee218a72d9464","tid":1210201,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2c412ff09b13cb63efdb2d6a94f14cfea2dcd6ee","tid":1210201,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到今日班義士覺得太少人會企硬<br />\n唔衝嘅覺得好無力<br />\n我好心痛"},{"pid":"0457b174fdabd9a01ffeeff7f043d48c3c36da4a","tid":1210201,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2243fcf97f70964d81e6b9a3ef4c3a15af9ca683","tid":1210201,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}